{"tid":2023952,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到今日仲唔肯用Twitter 嘅，你地根本就係偽黃","createTime":"2020-05-19T10:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T07:00:10.000Z","uid":27725,"like":30,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5458185a5d47a611f7392b68d7fc4524db82101d","tid":2023952,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"作為一個基本上日日用social media 嘅後生仔，你無可能唔識用Twitter。你死都唔踏出依一步，你仲話你自己係黃？你只係懶，一直俾籍口自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你得條底褲好撚黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 只係第一步，之後嘅國際戰線應該要進化到更深層，更深遠，直至真正嘅香港獨立<br />\n而家叫你用多個social media 都唔肯，每人每日用半個鐘，效果已經好好。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Twitter 戰線，起碼每日活躍用戶要有20萬，先叫達標<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 係好撚基本"},{"pid":"29173d1f9f1f18c1e682f719cb38934fa92bbcbc","tid":2023952,"uid":27725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"屌曬所有唔撚用Twitter 嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4d4317251c61803bc72a2de13d00d40ed5a150","tid":2023952,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig story圍爐打飛機冇用架"},{"pid":"25862dc5b590af4221d32206a099b06fe8cb02fd","tid":2023952,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"